OL,3,CThe oil shock looks over, but we'll be
OL,4,Ccounting the cost of this war for a
OL,5,Cwhile
OL,7,FJoel Hill explains the economic shock
OL,8,Fthe closure had on the world - and why
OL,9,Fthe aftershocks will continue despite
OL,10,Fa pending US-Iran peace deal
OL,12,F"Ships of the world, start your
OL,13,Fengines. Let the oil flow," wrote
OL,14,FPresident Trump overnight on Truth
OL,15,FSocial, raising the prospect of a
OL,16,Flasting end to the conflict that the
OL,17,FUS and Israel began 107 days ago.
