OL,3,CThe oil shock looks over, but we'll be
OL,4,Ccounting the cost of this war for a
OL,5,Cwhile
OL,7,FThe latest tracking data from
OL,8,FMarineTraffic shows that there were
OL,9,Fstill about 500 stranded tankers and
OL,10,Fcargo vessels in the Strait of Hormuz
OL,11,Fon Monday morning.
OL,13,FThere hasn't been a rush to leave so
OL,14,Ffar.
OL,16,FThe Disha, a Maltese-registered ship
OL,17,Fcarrying liquefied natural gas, made
OL,18,Fthe journey through the Strait bound
OL,19,Ffor India. The tanker passed through
OL,20,FIranian waters early Monday morning,
OL,21,Fone of only two transits by lunchtime.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
