OL,3,CThe oil shock looks over, but we'll be
OL,4,Ccounting the cost of this war for a
OL,5,Cwhile
OL,7,FIran has hijacked two cargo ships, and
OL,8,Fat least ten seafarers have been
OL,9,Fkilled.
OL,11,FThe market price of oil fell when
OL,12,Ftrading opened on Monday to $83 a
OL,13,Fbarrel.
OL,15,FThat's still around $10 higher than
OL,16,Fbefore the war began and could remain
OL,17,Felevated if it takes time for oil
OL,18,Fproduction to return to pre-war levels.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
