OL,3,CThe oil shock looks over, but we'll be
OL,4,Ccounting the cost of this war for a
OL,5,Cwhile
OL,7,FAmong them is Ras Laffan, which
OL,8,Fproduces around one-fifth of the
OL,9,Fworld's liquefied natural gas.
OL,11,FRepairs could take several years, and
OL,12,Fthe bill will stretch into the
OL,13,Fbillions of pounds.
OL,15,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
