OL,3,CThe oil shock looks over, but we'll be
OL,4,Ccounting the cost of this war for a
OL,5,Cwhile
OL,7,FThe fact that the US and Iran both
OL,8,Fseem keen on peace reduces fears of a
OL,9,Frecession-inducing economic shock.
OL,11,FBut we don't yet know whether peace
OL,12,Fwill last or, if it does, how long it
OL,13,Fwill take for oil and gas flows to
OL,14,Freturn to pre-war levels.
OL,16,FMeanwhile, inflation is already edging
OL,17,Fhigher, with further price rises still
OL,18,Fin the pipeline.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
